#: ../../content/getting-started/rebuilds.md:1
msgid "Understanding rebuilds"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/getting-started/rebuilds.md:3
msgid ""
"Completed stages for a package are not executed again when releng-tool is"
" re-run."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/getting-started/rebuilds.md:5
msgid ""
"Users looking to re-run a completed stage for a specific package need to "
"manually re-trigger the stage (e.g. [`releng-tool <pkg>-rebuild`](action-"
"pkg-rebuild), [`releng-tool <pkg>-reconfigure`](action-pkg-reconfigure), "
"[`releng-tool <pkg>-reinstall`](action-pkg-reinstall))."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/getting-started/rebuilds.md:10
msgid ""
"Users can also invoke [`releng-tool punch`](action-punch) for force re-"
"trigger all package stages."
msgstr ""

